In the Asphaltgold app you'll find everything you need in the sneaker and apparel world compact and clearly arranged. Our all-in-one solution allows you to participate in raffles as well as regular online shopping.

SMOOTHE SHOPPING-EXPERIENCE
Find the latest product highlights in our swipeable home feed. If you prefer to search specifically, it's easy via the basic menu, where you'll find all the categories you already know from our browser-based online store.

NEVER MISS A THING
Set up product-specific push messages for your desired raffles or restocks and be informed automatically and conveniently at the start.

SECURE AND WITHOUT RISK
We handle your payment information with the highest level of security. You are always in control of your participation and orders. As a payment method you can choose between Apple Pay, Paypal, Klarna and credit card.

descriptionHtml:
In the Asphaltgold app, you will find everything you need in the sneaker and fashion world in a compact and clear format. In addition to participating in Raffles and regular online shopping, our all-in-one solution enables optimal size advice from the Asphaltgold Fitting Room.

SMOOTH SHOPPING EXPERIENCE
You can find the latest product highlights in our scrollable home feed. If you prefer to search specifically, you can easily do this via the menu, where you will find all the categories you already know from our browser-based online store.

SHOP THE LOOK
Discover our curated styling suggestions and be inspired by the latest trends. With the “Shop The Look” function, you can discover the hottest outfits and order the matching products directly.

NEVER MISS ANYTHING AGAIN
Set up product-specific push notifications for your desired releases or restocks and be informed automatically and conveniently at the start.

YOUR SNEAKER, YOUR SIZE
Despite the same size information, sneakers vary depending on the brand and model. With the Asphaltgold Fitting Room, we want to help you find the right shoe size right away. Using a sneaker from your shoe cabinet, the Asphaltgold Fitting Room will recommend the right size for your desired sneaker.

SECURE AND RISK-FREE
We handle your payment information with the highest standards of security. You have control over your Raffle entries and orders at all times. You can choose between Apple Pay, PayPal and credit card as your payment method.
